<h1 class="hero-h">2026 fitness AI ROI <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">reference data.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Observational ROI data across the 10 most common AI agent workflows in fitness — lead nurture, no-show recovery, member retention, AI coaching, and more. Built from observation across multi-unit operators and franchisees. Specifically designed for fitness operators and franchisors building business cases for AI agent deployment. Citable; refreshed quarterly.</p>
